Package: MooseR
Title: Data Cleaning and Summary Utility Functions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("LisbonBulldog", email = "develop@lisbonbulldog.xyz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of utility functions for common data wrangling tasks,
    including column name cleaning, duplicate detection, uniqueness checks,
    quote removal, one-row summary tables for categorical and continuous variables,
    covariate balance comparison, stable de-identified ID generation, and date helpers.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/MooseWEB3/MooseR
BugReports: https://github.com/MooseWEB3/MooseR/issues
